title: Philippines GDP From Services
description: GDP From Services in Philippines increased to 3047107.89 PHP Million in the fourth quarter of 2021 from 2816492.98 PHP Million in the third quarter of 2021. GDP From Services in Philippines averaged 1774348.79 PHP Million from 2000 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 3069173.27 PHP Million in the fourth quarter of 2019 and a record low of 866882.21 PHP Million in the first quarter of 2000. This page provides - Philippines Gdp From Services- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Philippine Statistics Authority
